{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-038","title":"承诺担保","sectionId":"chapter-02","sectionTitle":"日常交际你最强","pageStart":209,"pageEnd":213,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":18,"duplicateEntryCount":15,"pages":[{"number":209,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"38 承诺担保"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"written guarantee书面保证","headword":"written guarantee"},{"type":"entry","text":"guarantor [ˌɡærənˈtɔː(r)]","headword":"guarantor"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.保证人"},{"type":"entry","text":"commit a crime犯罪，犯下罪行","headword":"commit a crime"}]},{"number":210,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"commitment [kəˈmɪtmənt]","headword":"commitment"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.承诺；承担的义务"},{"type":"note","text":"◎make a commitment承诺"},{"type":"entry","text":"professional commitment专业承诺","headword":"professional commitment"},{"type":"text","text":"assure sb. of sth. 向某人确保某事"},{"type":"text","text":"convince sb. of sth. 使某人确信某事"},{"type":"entry","text":"give a guarantee 做出保证","headword":"give a guarantee"}]},{"number":211,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"trusty [ˈtrʌsti]","headword":"trusty"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.可信赖的；可靠的"},{"type":"entry","text":"authenticity [ˌɔːθenˈtɪsəti]","headword":"authenticity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.真实性；可靠性"},{"type":"entry","text":"stipulated [ˈstɪpjuleɪtɪd]","headword":"stipulated"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.规定的"},{"type":"entry","text":"validly [ˈvælɪdli]","headword":"validly"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.合法地，正当地"},{"type":"entry","text":"advisable choice 明智的选择","headword":"advisable choice"},{"type":"entry","text":"keep one's word 信守诺言","headword":"keep one's word"},{"type":"entry","text":"make a promise 许下诺言","headword":"make a promise"},{"type":"entry","text":"under a vow 发过誓","headword":"under a vow"},{"type":"entry","text":"absolutely right 完全正确","headword":"absolutely right"}]},{"number":212,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"time delay延时","headword":"time delay"},{"type":"entry","text":"loss [lɒs]","headword":"loss"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.亏损"},{"type":"entry","text":"limited liability有限责任","headword":"limited liability"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Make a commitment to yourself. （对自己做一个承诺。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：I don't want to do this.（我不想这么做。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"}]},{"number":213,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"A：We'd like to get some information about mortgage loans. （我们"},{"type":"text","text":"想了解一些抵押贷款方面的信息。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Well, we generally lend 80% of the bank's appraised value on 30,"},{"type":"title","text":"35 or 40-year mortgages if the house is less than 10 years old .（嗯，如果"},{"type":"text","text":"房屋从建成至今尚未超过10年，我们一般借给买房者的数额是银行对"},{"type":"text","text":"房屋估价的80%，而贷款期为30、35或40年。）"}]}]}